column5: Does anyone have a map of Lac Seul on the northwest side by Ear Falls that I could temporarily use or does anyone know of a place where I can buy one from that is pretty detailed? Any information is greatly appreciated. Thank you

I asked the same question a couple months ago, and here's the response I was given:Smitty's phone: 807-222-3738Box 326Ear Falls, Ontatio POV 1TO~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~4 Seasons Sport Shop807-222-2200 (summer) 807-222-3030 (winter)Box 327Ear Falls, Ontario, Canada POV 1TO~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~Bratland's807-227-2668Hwy 17Vermillion Bay
try ministry of natural resourcessioux lookout807-737-1140the ministry used to sell maps but not sure if they still provide the service
